  23 Jun 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  xfce4-systemload-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Fix xfce4-dev-tools dep.

  25 Apr 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  xfce4-systemload-0.4.2.ebuild:
  We need to specify AT_M4DIR for xfce-extra/xfce4-dev-tools for eautoreconf
  and run intltoolize for another error during the build wrt bug 219250.

  21 Apr 2008; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  xfce4-systemload-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Run full eautoreconf, _not_ eautoconf, if the package does not only use
  autoconf but also aclocal. Closes bug #217800.

  24 Oct 2007; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org>
  xfce4-systemload-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Fix test suite and unrestrict it

  03 Jun 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  xfce4-systemload-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Add missing DOCS variable.

  15 Mar 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  xfce4-systemload-0.4.2.ebuild:
  RESTRICT="test" which is not supported by goodies upstream.

